        ],
        [
          "Martin/Maria Fontana",
          "Your pack priest - a Lasombra.   It is a secret of your pack that you all conspired to rescue them from their abusive sire.  It's a common trait you all share, but Fontana is the only one whose sire was True Sabbat when you effected your rescue."
        ],
        [
          "Cameron Spelman",
          "Newest member of your pack - the abused childe of a Camarilla Ventrue elder. You see them as a kindred spirit in the tensions they must struggle with in reconciling the awful experience they had with their sire and the habits of courtesy and courtliness that were instilled in them.  Still struggling to find a path and break away from their humanity - you are trying to bring them with you onto the Path of Caine."
        ],
